{"tid":895820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日睇新聞覺得香港真係冇得救","createTime":"2018-11-09T13:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T14:46:26.000Z","uid":63768,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"915ecd75f39b33d6906249252ae7308e0b81a903","tid":895820,"uid":63768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T13:16:26.000Z","msg":"雖然香港冇得救不嬲都唔係新聞 不過今日睇新聞真係好大感受<br />\n而家FCC果個外國人出黎幫香港人爭取新聞自由 言論自由&hellip;<br />\n香港人都好似冇乜感覺咁 <br />\n覺得自己乜都做唔倒<br />\n果個作家本身都唔知佢係咩人黎 <br />\n想係香港搞個講座都俾人撚到&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n明日大嶼俾政府強姦 都係叫兩聲就算<br />\n東涌變左don't ever go again就唔關我事<br />\nKong U變左香港市第一人民大學都唔緊要啦 我都grad咗<br />\n做雞俾人整痛都識叫唔好啦<br />\n香港人除咗俾人阻住返工 幾時先會識出黎講唔好<br />\n<br />\n想講係我個藍絲老竇都覺得今次入境on9<br />\n其實香港人可唔可以做返啲野<br />\n令政府知道<br />\n我地重視言論自由 新聞自由<br />\n睇住呢個地方咁沉淪落去真係好心痛&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd0a48b67a0a884798193ea1ce2d7806ca9c132","tid":895820,"uid":7790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"1997之後已經無救，只係有人後知後覺..."},{"pid":"ad08a47968bd96e461db337e657dc174d1df11d7","tid":895820,"uid":21034,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"想知樓主除左開post做左啲咩救港"},{"pid":"0b7f7be59eabc87e35f438b55f4fd1418e738020","tid":895820,"uid":220701,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ad08a47968bd96e461db337e657dc174d1df11d7","tid":895820,"uid":21034,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"想知樓主除左開post做左啲咩救港"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"我都想知你做過乜"},{"pid":"55464b3f43bbc17ceb74862a37ed12e1f215a970","tid":895820,"uid":21034,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0b7f7be59eabc87e35f438b55f4fd1418e738020","tid":895820,"uid":220701,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ad08a47968bd96e461db3